                    "Title": "淮安",
                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e06e023ddbcb4d9da7a6df183cb24527\");'><span id='e06e023ddbcb4d9da7a6df183cb24527_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，41岁</div><div id='e06e023ddbcb4d9da7a6df183cb24527' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年8月</a>　八月，完颜昌攻楚州，其为参谋军事，兼随军转运使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>　楚州久攻不下，其为金人作檄招降。<br /></div>"
